### Retrieve Product Bundle Information Based on an ID [GET /product-bundles{id}] 

+ Parameters

    + id (required, string) - Product bundle id

+ Request

    + Headers

            cid: 05e230bf-a9cf-4b31-bc54-d3a995f62526
            
+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "status": "SUCCESS",
                "data": {
